          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",

          "text": "This semester, our student volunteers have not only dedicated countless hours to community service but have also excelled academically.         {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8172-91d9-e59ec13f15ed",

          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",

        },

          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-819b-84f0-f6360fc11fe7",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Major: Biology"
        },

          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8153-80c5-ce5c5e52c1d5",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",

          "text": "GPA: 3.9"

          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Notable Courses: Genetics (A), Organic Chemistry II (A-), Biostatistics (A)"
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8109-a269-f99b6f379d48",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Professor's Note: Emma has consistently demonstrated a keen understanding of complex topics, often contributing insightful observations during lectures. Her participation in the Genetics research project was particularly commendable."
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-81f3-b483-e18895538e55",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "**Liam Johnson:**"
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-81e6-bb68-e2cb1c36e71d",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Major: Environmental Science"
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-81e1-8d9c-dada1ada4fc5",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,

          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Notable Courses: Climate Change Solutions (A), Environmental Policy (A-), Ecology (B+)"
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-812b-af9c-e912d53252d2",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Professor's Note: Liam's engagement in class discussions and his leadership in group projects stand out. He successfully led a workshop on sustainable practices at our local community center as part of his volunteer work."
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8112-8181-dff412c63606",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "**Sophia Martinez:**"
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-81a3-9d21-c30934af1169",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Major: Computer Science"

        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8180-a797-ed4545451b52",

          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Notable Courses: Algorithms (A), Database Systems (A), Software Engineering (A)"
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8149-9c3d-d4ef9eb9ea82",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Professor's Note: Sophia has excelled in her coursework, often going above and beyond on assignments. She has also been tutoring fellow students in coding, displaying both her knowledge and commitment to volunteerism."
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8172-b1c4-ffe6b4f26927",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",

          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",

          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Notable Courses: Modern American Literature (A-), Creative Writing (A), Literary Theory (B+)"

        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-811f-b492-d5b72b1868d2",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,
          "text": "Professor's Note: Noah's critical essays have been a highlight of the semester, showing deep analytical skills and creativity. He has volunteered to organize a series of poetry readings for the local community, blending his academic interests with service."
        },
        {
          "id": "1f40dc8f-a0db-8179-85d3-cffdd96b5061",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "created_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "last_edited_time": "2025-05-15T12:41:00.000Z",
          "has_children": false,

{"to":["sarah@helpinghands.org"],"subject":"Update on Student Volunteer Involvement","body":"Hi Sarah,

I hope you’re doing well. I wanted to share a brief update on our student volunteer’s involvement with Helping Hands Foundation.

• Commitment: The student has continued to attend each outreach session regularly, often arriving early to help with set-up and staying afterward for clean-up.
• Initiative: They have recently taken the lead on organizing activity stations during weekend events and have been quick to step into new roles whenever extra assistance is needed.
• Peer Support: New volunteers consistently mention how welcomed and prepared they feel thanks to the student’s guidance and positive attitude.

Overall, their dedication and professionalism have made a noticeable difference, and their contribution is highly valued by everyone on site.

Please let me know if you’d like any additional information or if there are new areas where the student could focus their efforts.

Thank you for your continued partnership.

Best regards,
[Your Name]"}
